- [x] Request → Review → Approval → Disbursement (logical only)
- [x] Multi-party approval (if required)
- [x] Audit trail for approvals

### Interest Control
- [ ] Group sets interest rate
- [ ] System enforces:
  - [ ] Upper cap (anti-exploitation)
  - [ ] Warning if exceeding recommended range

### Repayment Logic
- [x] Scheduled repayments tracked (Automated via `LoanRepaymentService`)
- [ ] Late repayment penalties configurable
- [ ] Loan default handling defined

